40|$|The EU-funded project VALERI {{aimed to}} {{validate}} the use of mobile manipulators for aerospace production. This paper focuses on the development and application of a 2 1 / 2 D workspace monitoring system for safeguarding the tool when working {{in close proximity to}} human operators. The sensor set up, the operational principles, and functional tests when used as a <b>safety</b> <b>sensor</b> will be described in this contribution...|$|E
